AttributeList.Text: ============================================================================= This module is used in Applications when a roller one way two speed equipped with SEW MoviDrive is needed. The roller can support single body tranport and simultanious transport. The roller is equipped with a standard sensor setting, one stop High Speed and one at the front for dual speed transport. The roller uses standard handshaking signals to accomplish an infeed transfer with the previous transport system and an outfeed with the next transport system. The roller will support automatic Mode and manual Mode according specific guidelines. The outfeed will be master over the infeed. Alarm "body not in Position" is also generated. All Alarms coming from sub-functions, TrfIn, TrfOut & LMotor2W2S-MDXPNSynch or from local Alarm are summarized to give also the global Alarm A, B, C & D to upper level. =============================================================================
